name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: THYNK Crosswalk Validator for Medical Codes

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Streamline & enhance medical coding workflows with the Crosswalk Validator. Supports ICD-10-AM, ICD-10-CM, SBS, ACHI.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Streamline & enhance medical coding workflows with the Crosswalk Validator, a powerful Chrome extension designed for accurate validation of crosswalks between different medical code systems. Supports ICD-10-AM, ICD-10-CM, SBS, ACHI.
